        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "Role: You are an expert HTML Email Developer.\nTask: Convert the provided plain text email body into a premium, dark-themed responsive HTML email.\n\n### DESIGN SPECIFICATIONS:\n1. Background Color: Set the main wrapper background to #030C1B.\n2. Text Color: Use #FFFFFF (White) or #E0E0E0 (Light Grey) for all body text to ensure high readability.\n3. Styles: Use ONLY inline CSS. \n4. Layout: \n   - Max-width: 600px, centered.\n   - Padding: 40px for desktop, 20px for mobile.\n   - Font: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif.\n5. Elements:\n   - Wrap the text in <p> tags with line-height: 1.6.\n   - Headers should be bold and clearly separated.\n   - Use a subtle border or secondary color for call-to-action buttons if present.\n\n### CONSTRAINTS:\n- Output ONLY the final HTML code.\n- Do not include markdown code blocks (no ```html).\n- Do not include any preamble or conversational text.\n\n### INPUT:\n[The text body to be converted]"
        }
      },
